        },
        "committer": {
          "name": "Qian Yingjin",
          "email": "qian@ddn.com",
          "date": "2022-08-01 09:46:27.000000000",
          "tz": -240
        },
        "subject": "LU-13564 wbc: check low inode threshold for MDT",
        "message": "LU-13564 wbc: check low inode threshold for MDT\n\nIn this patch, we add a new parameter \"mdt_iavail_low\".\nWe check the inode space of each MDT before determine to cache the\nfile on the client under WBC. When the available inode number of\none MDT is less than this value \"mdt_iavail_low\", the client will\nstop to cache the newly creating file under WBC.\nWhen set this value with 0, the client will skip this check.\n\nAdd sanity-wbc/114 to verify it.\n\nSigned-off-by: Qian Yingjin <qian@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: Icc7b3ae06e5afccbbdd6680e1953565d12314b2d\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
